premise_source_doc_sentence: Now there are several competing digital 3D formats including Dolby 3D , XpanD 3D , Panavision 3D , MasterImage 3D and IMAX 3D .
Development of Avatar began in 1994 , when Cameron wrote an 80-page treatment for the film .

Step Up 3D premiered in Hollywood at the El Capitan Theater on August 2 , 2010 and was subsequently released worldwide on August 6 , 2010 , through conventional 2D and 3D  (  in RealD 3D , Dolby 3D , and XpanD 3D  )  formats .

The film made extensive use of new motion capture filming techniques , and was released for traditional viewing , 3D viewing  (  using the RealD 3D , Dolby 3D , XpanD 3D , and IMAX 3D formats  )  , and for `` 4D '' experiences in select South Korean theaters .
The film was released in RealD 3D , XpanD 3D , and Dolby 3D with Max Giwa and Dania Pasquini directing it .
